The '''CINOA Prize''' is a prize awarded yearly to art historians by [[CINOA]], the international confederation of art dealers, "in recognition of an academic publication or a remarkable contribution to furthering the cultural preservation through art works in a CINOA member country".<ref>CINOA, [http://www.cinoa.org/index.pl?id=2218;isa=Category;op=show "The CINOA Prize"] (page retrieved November 24th, 2006).</ref>
